A sequence of polynomials is given by $p_(n)(x)=a_(n+2)x^(2)+a_(n+1)x-a_(n)$,
for $n>=0$, where $a_(0)=a_(1)=1$ and, for $n>=0$, $a_(n+2)=a_(n+1)+a_(n)$.
Denote by $r_(n)$ and $s_(n)$ the roots of $p_(n)(x)=0,$ with $r_(n)<= s_(n)$.
Find $display(lim_(n -> infinity) r_n)$ and $display(lim_(n -> infinity) s_n)$.
